[/size][size=3]For an ice theme series, I made "Manouche". Her makeup is turquise/blue and her tint is also a bit bluish.

[youtube]W8tFZvuuQEI[/youtube]
Visit me on [url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoWsDNCJ0vqTRJ17k3-1jbg]Youtube[/url]

[/url]

[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/82835-0-1490016872.png[/img]

Recommended (optional):

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32986/]Mature skin texture and body for UNP(B) 7BASE CBBE Vanilla


[/url]Installation: 

Use NMM to easily install file
- or -
1. download and unzip the .RAR and search for: "Manouche.jslot"
2. locate your presets folder in your Skyrim Directory (ex. C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\common\skyrim\data\SKSE\plugins\CharGen\Presets)
3. put "Manouche.jslot" in your presets folder.
4. open the game and type "^" to open the console.
5. type "showracemenu" to activate RaceMenu,
choose Nord race.
6. you´ll find "Manouche" at the presets slider.

Appearance will vary depending on the meshes/textures/ENB you use.

I´m using a combination of
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71293/]GrimTale ENB[/url] &
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/46320/]Megatherium ENB

[/url]My other preset:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81718/]"Bishop"
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/82911/]"Rebekka"[/url]

Permission:
